ssage will override your social post content.":["Zde napi\u0161te vlastn\u00ed zpr\u00e1vu pro sv\u00e9 publikum na soci\u00e1ln\u00edch s\u00edt\u00edch. Tato zpr\u00e1va nahrad\u00ed obsah va\u0161eho p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku na soci\u00e1ln\u00edch s\u00edt\u00edch."],"Invalid media":["Neplatn\u00e9 m\u00e9dium"],"Invalid dimensions":["Neplatn\u00e9 rozm\u011bry"],"Video too short":["Video je p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 kr\u00e1tk\u00e9"],"Video too long":["Video je p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 dlouh\u00e9"],"File too big":["Soubor je p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 velk\u00fd"],"Please fix the broken connections or disconnect them to create more connections.":["Opravte nefunk\u010dn\u00ed p\u0159ipojen\u00ed nebo je odpojte, abyste mohli vytvo\u0159it dal\u0161\u00ed p\u0159ipojen\u00ed."],"Fix social media connection\u0004Fix connection":["Opravit p\u0159ipojen\u00ed"],"Fix the social media connections\u0004Fix connections":["Opravit p\u0159ipojen\u00ed"],"Want to share to other networks? Use our Manual Sharing feature from the editor.":["Chcete sd\u00edlet na jin\u00fdch s\u00edt\u00edch? Pou\u017eijte na\u0161i funkci ru\u010dn\u00edho sd\u00edlen\u00ed v editoru."],"Comma to separate list of social media platforms\u0004,":[","],"Colon to display before the list of social media platforms\u0004:":[":"],"You can use our <link>Manual Sharing<\/link> feature instead.":["M\u00edsto toho m\u016f\u017eete pou\u017e\u00edt na\u0161i funkci <link>Ru\u010dn\u00ed sd\u00edlen\u00ed<\/link>."],"Threads link preview requires an image to be set for the post. Please add an image to see the preview.":["Pro n\u00e1hled odkaz\u016f ve vl\u00e1knech je nutn\u00e9 nastavit obr\u00e1zek pro p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek. P\u0159idejte obr\u00e1zek, abyste mohli zobrazit n\u00e1hled."],"Generate an image with AI":["Vytvo\u0159te obr\u00e1zek pomoc\u00ed AI"],"Insert image":["Vlo\u017eit obr\u00e1zek"],"Creating image\u2026":["Vytv\u00e1\u0159en\u00ed obr\u00e1zku\u2026"],"Image generation costs %d requests per image. You don't have enough requests to generate another image.":["Generov\u00e1n\u00ed obr\u00e1zku stoj\u00ed %d po\u017eadavk\u016f na obr\u00e1zek. Nem\u00e1te dostatek po\u017eadavk\u016f na generov\u00e1n\u00ed dal\u0161\u00edho obr\u00e1zku."],"Image saved to media library.":["Obr\u00e1zek ulo\u017een do knihovny m\u00e9di\u00ed."],"Add Threads connection":["P\u0159idat p\u0159ipojen\u00ed Threads"],"Increase your presence in social media by sharing your posts automatically to Threads.":["Zvy\u0161te svou p\u0159\u00edtomnost na soci\u00e1ln\u00edch m\u00e9di\u00edch automatick\u00fdm sd\u00edlen\u00edm sv\u00fdch p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f na Threads."],"Share posts to your Threads feed.":["Sd\u00edlejte p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky ve sv\u00e9m kan\u00e1lu Threads."],"The name of the social media network - threads.net\u0004Threads":["Threads"],"Threads profile image":["Profilov\u00fd obr\u00e1zek Threads"],"This platform is no longer supported.":["Tato platforma ji\u017e nen\u00ed podporov\u00e1na."],"Updating account":["Aktualizace \u00fa\u010dtu"],"Error updating account.":["Chyba p\u0159i aktualizaci \u00fa\u010dtu."],"Account updated successfully.":["\u00da\u010det byl \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b aktualizov\u00e1n."],"Error connecting account.":["Chyba p\u0159i p\u0159ipojov\u00e1n\u00ed \u00fa\u010dtu."],"%s account connected successfully.":["\u00da\u010det %s byl \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b p\u0159ipojen."],"Error disconnecting account.":["Chyba p\u0159i odpojov\u00e1n\u00ed \u00fa\u010dtu."],"Account disconnected successfully.":["\u00da\u010det byl \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b odpojen."],"To share to Mastodon please enter your Mastodon username below, then click connect.":["Chcete-li sd\u00edlet na Mastodonu, zadejte n\u00ed\u017ee sv\u00e9 u\u017eivatelsk\u00e9 jm\u00e9no Mastodon a klikn\u011bte na tla\u010d\u00edtko P\u0159ipojit."],"Share with your network.":["Sd\u00edlejte se svou s\u00edt\u00ed."],"Add Tumblr connection":["P\u0159idat p\u0159