usiness."],"Requirements for connecting Instagram:":["Po\u017eadavky pro p\u0159ipojen\u00ed Instagramu:"],"Drive engagement and save time by automatically sharing images to Instagram when you publish blog posts.":["Zvy\u0161te zapojen\u00ed u\u017eivatel\u016f a u\u0161et\u0159ete \u010das automatick\u00fdm sd\u00edlen\u00edm obr\u00e1zk\u016f na Instagramu p\u0159i publikov\u00e1n\u00ed blogov\u00fdch p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f."],"Share to your Instagram Business account.":["Sd\u00edlejte na sv\u00e9m \u00fa\u010dtu Instagram Business."],"Add Facebook connection":["P\u0159idat p\u0159ipojen\u00ed k Facebooku"],"<strong>Connect<\/strong> to automatically share posts on your Facebook page.":["<strong>P\u0159ipojte se<\/strong> a automaticky sd\u00edlejte p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky na sv\u00e9 str\u00e1nce na Facebooku."],"Share to your pages":["Sd\u00edlet na sv\u00fdch str\u00e1nk\u00e1ch"],"This Mastodon account is already connected":["Tento \u00fa\u010det Mastodon je ji\u017e propojen\u00fd."],"Invalid Mastodon username":["Neplatn\u00e9 u\u017eivatelsk\u00e9 jm\u00e9no Mastodon"],"%d connections":["%d p\u0159ipojen\u00ed"],"This connection is added by a site administrator.":["Toto propojen\u00ed p\u0159id\u00e1v\u00e1 spr\u00e1vce webu."],"Connect more":["P\u0159ipojte se v\u00edce"],"Manage Jetpack Social connections":["Spr\u00e1va soci\u00e1ln\u00edch p\u0159ipojen\u00ed Jetpack"],"Connection confirmation":["Potvrzen\u00ed p\u0159ipojen\u00ed"],"Already connected":["Ji\u017e p\u0159ipojeno"],"No accounts\/pages found.":["Nebyly nalezeny \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 \u00fa\u010dty\/str\u00e1nky."],"Message shown when there are no connections found to connect\u0004No more accounts\/pages found.":["\u017d\u00e1dn\u00e9 dal\u0161\u00ed \u00fa\u010dty\/str\u00e1nky nebyly nalezeny."],"You can change this later.":["Toto m\u016f\u017eete zm\u011bnit pozd\u011bji."],"If enabled, the connection will be available to all administrators, editors, and authors.":["Pokud je tato mo